0. Validate that LibaryDemo.sol works

0b. Add dictionaries to IPFS and then put the hash of those dictionaries in the contract with a getter.

1. Deploy your application onto one of the test networks. Include a document called deployed_addresses.txt that describes where your contracts live (which testnet and address).

2. You can verify your contract source code using etherscan for the appropriate testnet https://etherscan.io/verifyContract 

3. Sign transactions using MetaMask or uPort

4. Record your screen as you demo the application, showing and explaining how you included the required components.
